    "body": "Hey @MysticRyuujin, as far as I can tell these are all issues that are about the version of MyCrypto that's currently in production. You can find the issue queue for that over at https://github.com/MyCryptoHQ/mycrypto.com, this is for the not-yet-released beta version. I think you'll find problems 1 and 2 aren't an issue in the beta.\r\n\r\nAs for 3, while I think their UI is nicer, I think the UX of having one thing to paste in is a good deal more convenient than having to paste in a bunch of stuff. But I also agree that our verify is a little... lackluster at the moment.\r\n\r\nI'm going to close this issue since most of it is in reference to the production site, but if you want to make a new issue about sprucing up verify, go ahead. Thanks for posting!",
